name: Keep Calm  Play Games
summary:
This week we discuss: Keep Calm and Play Games

We are devoting an entire episode to growing CALMNESS! This is a big topic and often the starting place to crack many, many, many dog training struggles.

The emotion of calmness goes hand in hand with your dog behaving entirely appropriately.

You can never have too much calmness, a dog can never be too calm. CALMNESS IS KING!

Listen in to learn how you can grow more calmness in your dog.
